OL,3,CMaternity unit closed over safety
OL,4,Cfears to reopen
OL,6,FMaternity and paediatric units at
OL,7,FYeovil District Hospital, which were
OL,8,Fclosed due to concerns over the care
OL,9,Fof babies and children, are set to
OL,10,Freopen, subject to meeting specific
OL,11,Fcriteria.
OL,13,FSomerset NHS Foundation Trust closed
OL,14,Fthe Special Care Baby Unit and the
OL,15,Finpatient maternity service on 19 May
OL,16,F2025, stating it could not "safely run
OL,17,Fthe unit" or "safely provide care
OL,18,Fduring labour and birth".
