OL,3,CMaternity unit closed over safety
OL,4,Cfears to reopen
OL,6,FThe trust said both units are
OL,7,Fscheduled to reopen on 21 April 2026,
OL,8,Falmost a year after the units were
OL,9,Fclosed for an initial period of six
OL,10,Fmonths.
OL,12,FSince the services closed, the trust
OL,13,Fsaid more than 350 babies who would
OL,14,Fhave been born in Yeovil have been
OL,15,Fborn elsewhere, mostly at Musgrove
OL,16,FPark Hospital and Dorset County
OL,17,FHospital. Both hospitals are more than
OL,18,F20 miles away from Yeovil District
OL,19,FHospital.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
