OL,6,FIt also found that some staff failed
OL,7,Fto follow infection control
OL,8,Fprinciples, like washing their hands
OL,9,Fbefore administering care.
OL,11,FPeter Lewis, chief executive of
OL,12,FSomerset NHS Foundation Trust, said "a
OL,13,Fhuge amount of work" has been carried
OL,14,Fout to address the safety concerns.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
