OL,4,Cfears to reopen
OL,6,F"This involves working with our new
OL,7,Fpaediatric consultants, who join us
OL,8,Ffrom November 2025 through to March
OL,9,F2026, and our maternity colleagues,
OL,10,Fmany of whom are working in maternity
OL,11,Fservices at Musgrove Park Hospital and
OL,12,FDorset County Hospital, without
OL,13,Fdestabilising those maternity
OL,14,Fservices."
OL,16,F"We have set out the essential
OL,17,Fcriteria that must be in place to
OL,18,Freopen services, and improvement
OL,19,Fcriteria which will continue to be
OL,20,Fdelivered and embedded following
OL,21,Freopening."
